\c 20
\s Kurwara kwaHezekia nekupora kwake
\p
\v 1 Mumazuva iwayo Hezekia wakarwara zvekufa. Muporofita Isaya mwanakomana waAmozi ndokusvika kwaari, ndokuti kwaari: ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha: Raira imbayako, nokuti uchafa, uye haungararami.
\v 2 Zvino wakatendeusira chiso chake kumadziro, ndokunyengetera kuna Jehovha, achiti:
\v 3 Ndinokukumbirisai, Jehovha, dorangarirai kuti ndakafamba pamberi penyu muchokwadi uye nemoyo wakapererachokwadi nomoyo wese, ndikaita zvakanaka pamberi penyu. Hezekia akachema kwazvo.
\v 4 Zvino Isaya wakange achigere kubuda paruvazhe rwapakati, shoko raJehovha rikauya kwaari, richiti:
\v 5 Dzokazve, undoti kuna Hezekia, mutungamiriri wavanhu vangu: Zvanzi naJehovha Mwari waDhavhidhi baba vako: Ndanzwa kunyengetera kwako, ndaona misodzi yako; zvino tarira, ndichakuporesa; nezuva rechitatu uchakwira kuimba yaJehovha.
\v 6 Ndichawedzera pamazuva ako makore ane gumi namashanu; ndichakurwira iwe neguta rino paruoko rwamambo weAsiriya, ndichadzivira guta rino nokuda kwangu, uye nokuda kwaDhavhidhi muranda wangu.
\p
\v 7 Ipapo Isaya akati: Uyai nebundu ramawonde. Ivo vakauya naro, vakariisa pamamota, akapora.
\p
\v 8 Zvino Hezekia akati kuna Isaya: Chiratidzo chichava cheiko kuti Jehovha uchandiporesa, ndikwire kumba kwaJehovha nezuva rechitatu here?
\v 9 Isaya akati: Ichi chichava chiratidzo chaJehovha kwauri, kuti Jehovha uchaita sezvaakataura. Unoda kuti mumvuri upfuurire mberi mitaro inegumi, kana udzoke mitaro inegumi here?
\v 10 Hezekia akapindura, akati: Zvakareruka kuti mumvuri upfuurire mberi mitaro inegumi; kwete, mumvuri ngaudzoke mitaro inegumi.
\v 11 Ipapo muporofita akadana kuna Jehovha, akadzosera mumvuri shure mitaro inegumi pachiratidzo chenguva chaAhazi.
\p
\v 12 Zvino nenguva iyo Bherodhaki- bharadhani mwanakomana waBharadhani, mambo weBhabhironi, akatuma tsamba nechipo kuna Hezekia; nokuti wakange anzwa kuti Hezekia wairwara.
\v 13 Hezekia akavanzwa, akavaratidza imba yese yakange ine zvinokosha zvake, sirivha, negoridhe, nezvinonhuhwira, namafuta anokosha, neimba yaiva nenhumbi dzake dzokurwa nadzo, nezvese zvakange zviri pafuma yake; kwakange kusisina chinhu mumba make, kana muushe hwake hwese, chavasina kuratidzwa naHezekia.
\p
\v 14 Zvino muporofita Isaya akasvika kuna mambo Hezekia, akati kwaari: Ko varume ava vakati kudini? Vasvika kwauri vachibvepiko? Hezekia akati: Vabva kunyika iri kure, Bhabhironi.
\v 15 Akati: Vakawonei mumba mako? Hezekia akapindura, akati: Vakaona zvese zviri mumba mangu, hakune chinhu pakati pefuma yangu chandisina kuvaratidza.
\v 16 Ipapo Isaya akati kuna Hezekia: Inzwa shoko raJehovha.
\v 17 Tarira, mazuva achasvika, nenguva iyo zvese zviri mumba mako nezvese zvakaunganidzwa namadzibaba ako kusvikira zuva ranhasi zvichaiswa Bhabhironi; hakuna chinhu chichasiiwa, ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha.
\v 18 Vamwe vavanakomana vako, vachabva kwauri, vauchabereka, vachatapwa, vachava vatenwa mumba mamambo weBhabhironi.
\v 19 Ipapo Hezekia akati kuna Isaya, Shoko raJehovha, ramataura, rakanaka haro. Akatiwo: Ko handizvo here, kana rugare nechokwadi zviripo hazvo pamazuva angu?
\p
\v 20 Zvino mamwe mabasa aHezekia, nesimba rake, nokuita kwake dziva nomugero, nokusvitsa kwake mvura muguta, hazvina kunyorwa here mubhuku yaMakoronike amadzimambo aJudha?
\v 21 Hezekia akarara namadzibaba ake, Manase mwanakomana wake akamutevera paushe.
